main event: A UFO sighting was reported 30 miles west of Tripoli, Libya on February 16, 1957.
interesting points: The observer did not send the original report., There was only one object reported in the sighting., The duration of the observation was brief., No physical evidence was available to support the sighting., Case evaluation was unable to be performed due to insufficient data.
witness description: Original report not submitted; further witness details unknown.
